article.headline: Shogbonyo scores 16 in Denver's 86-63 victory over Colorado Christian
article.description: — Nicholas Shogbonyo scored 16 points as Denver beat Colorado Christian 86-63 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Shogbonyo scores 16 in Denver's 86-63 victory over Colorado Christian
article.story: DENVER -- — Nicholas Shogbonyo scored 16 points as Denver beat Colorado Christian 86-63 on Thursday night. Shogbonyo had six rebounds for the Pioneers (2-2). Josh Pickett scored 15 points while going 5 of 6 and 5 of 5 from the free-throw line and added six rebounds. Isaiah Addo-Ankrah finished 4 of 5 from 3-point range to finish with 14 points. Tate Odvody finished with 16 points for the Cougars. Colorado Christian also got 13 points from Bradley Land. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
